{"type":null,"faqId":49841,"title":"华为手机是否支持在市场上买的耳机的三键线控功能","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body34423584\"><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264494__p66494603\">华为手机都是支持耳机的三键线控的。目前市场上大多数的三键线控耳机都可以在华为手机上正常使用。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264494__p61580518\">当然也有少部分厂商耳机无法在华为手机上正常使用线控功能，如：苹果耳机。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022264494__p17353758\">为了让你有更好的音频体验及线控操作体验，建议您使用华为原装耳机。</p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022264494","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615544000,"seriesProductName":"NXT-AL10A,NXT-AL10B,NXT-AL10C,NXT-CL00A,NXT-DL00A,NXT-TL00A","visitedTimes":29,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"三键线控,华为手机","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}